# Live AI chat for the in-game V.I.S.H. lab assistant.
# Leave unset to use the built-in scripted (offline) chat — the game works
# fully without it. To go live:
#   1. cd functions && node buildPrompt.js
#   2. firebase deploy --only functions   (needs the GEN_AI_B secret set)
#   3. put the deployed portfolioChat URL here and rebuild
# VITE_CHAT_ENDPOINT=https://<region>-<project>.cloudfunctions.net/portfolioChat
